It has to be highlighted that reported data regarding COVID-19 exhibit high variability among outbreaks or are even inconsistent. Thus the parameter values could be subject to changes as further knowledge on the infection is attained. Moreover, parameters may suffer changes in time due to different public health policies implemented to fight against the spread of COVID-19. The simulations are performed with the initially estimated values given in Tables 1 and 2 for the specific demographic case of the Madrid Region (Comunidad de Madrid). Table 2
